165
00:09:12,860 --> 00:09:14,270
Kenapa sampai sekarang belum muncul?

166
00:09:15,700 --> 00:09:18,940
Pangeran, kau merindukan Putri, 'kan?

167
00:09:20,870 --> 00:09:22,340
